# AetherNexus Build-Out Walkthrough

## Summary

All 7 phases of the AetherNexus organism are complete. **22/22 tests passing**, zero warnings, GPU kernel dispatching on Apple M1 Pro at **389.6 tok/s** — 4.2× the Yellowpaper's 92 tok/s target.

## Phase 7 Benchmark Results

```
Device:           Apple M1 Pro
Iterations:       1000
KV tokens/step:   1280 (64 hot blocks + 16 cold blocks × 16 tok/block)

Total time:       2566.91 ms
Avg latency:      2.567 ms/token
Throughput:       389.6 tok/s

✅ Meets Yellowpaper target (≥92 tok/s)
```

