## Phase 7 Key Changes

- **Kernel**: Bound dictionary as [buffer(7)](file:///Users/kaizenpro/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/metal-0.30.0/src/encoder.rs#1562-1565), replaced placeholder with real `V ≈ Σ_k C_k · D[kv_head][idx_k][dim]`
- **Launcher**: Full Metal pipeline: Device → Library → Function → Pipeline → Encode → Dispatch → Readback
- **f16 fix**: Resolved Rust 2024 native [f16](file:///Users/kaizenpro/Desktop/aether_nexus/nexus-core/src/weaver.rs#162-167) / `half::f16` conflict using type alias
- **Benchmark**: 1000 iterations with 10-iteration warmup, tok/s + Yellowpaper comparison
